					</Bold>
					<LineBreak/>
					<Run Text='(1) A roll of 01, 02, or 03 is always a KO regardless of modifiers.'></Run>
					<LineBreak/>
					<Run Text='(2) Dice roll modifiers apply only To KO numbers. The numbers rolled before any modifications determine whether smoke is placed or not.'></Run>
					<LineBreak/>
					<Run Text='(3) During fog or falling snow '></Run>
					<InlineUIContainer>
						<Button Content='Weather' FontFamily='Courier New'  FontSize='8'></Button>
					</InlineUIContainer>
